• You could get early access to test Snapchat products or features

• We’ll ask some questions about you and your experience using Snapchat

We will use your responses to help identify what product engagement data to study and to improve our products to make Snapchat more fair and inclusive. For example, your responses might help us identify how people with certain physical characteristics interact with a specific feature, such as a Lens, so we can work on making it more inclusive. We’ll keep your responses for as long as we’re conducting our inclusivity research or until you decide to opt out. You can easily opt out by deselecting the button in the top right-hand corner. You can also change your answers at any time, in which case we’ll delete your previous responses.

If you change your mind and want to continue to help make our products more inclusive, you can rejoin the panel at any time by opting in in the top right-hand corner.

If you choose to opt out of the Made For Me Panel, your individual responses to our survey questions will be deleted, but we may still use your responses in the aggregate for future research about creating inclusive products.
